OL,3,CProtest told introduction of new
OL,4,Clegacy laws is 'day of shame'
OL,6,FThe beginning of new legacy
OL,7,Farrangements which shut down some
OL,8,FTroubles-era inquests represents a
OL,9,F"day of shame", Sinn Fein MP John
OL,10,FFincane has said.
OL,12,FMr Finucane addressed a protest
OL,13,Foutside the headquarters of the
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Office in Belfast
OL,15,Fcity centre, where he vowed that the
OL,16,Ffamilies of Troubles victims would
OL,17,Fnever give up the search for truth and
OL,18,Fjustice.
