OL,6,FThe new Independent Commission for
OL,7,FReconciliation and Information
OL,8,FRecovery (ICRIR), became operational
OL,9,Fon Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe ICRIR was created by the
OL,12,FGovernment's Legacy Act which received
OL,13,Froyal assent last year despite
OL,14,Fwidespread opposition from political
OL,15,Fparties, victims' organisations in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland and the Irish
OL,17,Fgovernment.
