OL,6,FAll new civil litigation and inquests
OL,7,Finto Troubles deaths which have not
OL,8,Fcompleted oral evidence will be
OL,9,Fstopped.
OL,11,FBereaved families, victims and certain
OL,12,Fpublic authorities can request the
OL,13,FICRIR carry out an investigation.
OL,15,FAround 100 people gathered outside the
OL,16,FNIO to protest against the changes.
