OL,6,FMany carried placards and photographs
OL,7,Fof family members who were killed. A
OL,8,Flarge black coffin bearing the word
OL,9,FJustice was laid at the door of the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,FMr Finucane said: "This is very much a
OL,13,Fday of shame. This is a day when legal
OL,14,Fchallenges in our courts officially
OL,15,Fcome to an end.
OL,17,F"Challenges that have been taken by
OL,18,Ffamilies who on some occasions have
OL,19,Fbeen waiting up to five decades for
OL,20,Fthe simple right to ask their
OL,21,Fquestions in a court room.
