OL,6,F"For the very simple basic democratic
OL,7,Fright to have an inquest for their
OL,8,Floved ones.
OL,10,F"We know the amount of inquests that
OL,11,Fhave not been able to conclude. They
OL,12,Fhaven't been able to conclude because
OL,13,Fthe British Government and their
OL,14,Fagencies knew that this day was coming.
OL,16,F"They knew and they were incentivised
OL,17,Fto delay and frustrate even more so
OL,18,Fthan they had done over the previous
OL,19,Ffive decades.
