OL,6,F"The British Government have today
OL,7,Fofficially removed the independence of
OL,8,Four courts in looking at our past."
OL,10,FMr Finucane's father Pat was murdered
OL,11,Fby loyalists in 1989.
OL,13,FThe Sinn Fein MP said the Legacy Act
OL,14,Fhad been introduced as an "obstacle in
OL,15,Fthe way of families finding truth".
OL,17,FHe also predicted that the new
OL,18,Farrangements would not be in place for
OL,19,Flong.
