OL,6,FHe said: "It has already been tested
OL,7,Fin our domestic courts and has been
OL,8,Fshown to be flawed.
OL,10,F"We await the outcome of the inter-
OL,11,Fgovernment state case taken by the
OL,12,FIrish Government."
OL,14,F"We wait to see whether a British
OL,15,FLabour government elected in the next
OL,16,Felection stand by their commitment to
OL,17,Frepeal this legislation."
OL,19,FThe protest was also addressed by
OL,20,FDamian Brown, the grandson of murder
OL,21,Fvictim Sean Brown.
