OL,6,FIn March, a legacy inquest into the
OL,7,Fdeath of the GAA official was halted
OL,8,Fwhen a coroner said his ability to
OL,9,Fexamine the killing had been
OL,10,Fcompromised by the extent of
OL,11,Fconfidential state material being
OL,12,Fexcluded from the proceedings on
OL,13,Fnational security grounds.
OL,15,FDuring a hearing it emerged that state
OL,16,Fagents were among more than 25 people
OL,17,Flinked by intelligence to the murder
OL,18,Fof Mr Brown in 1997.
