OL,6,FThe Government has since launched
OL,7,Flegal action over how the coroner
OL,8,Fdealt with a Public Interest Immunity
OL,9,F(PII) process in the case.
OL,11,FMr Brown told the rally: "We invested
OL,12,Four full faith in the inquest process.
OL,14,F"An inquest being the most
OL,15,Ffundamental, rudimentary, perfunctory
OL,16,Fof legal processes that the state must
OL,17,Fconclude when a life is taken in the
OL,18,Fmanner in which Sean's was stolen from
OL,19,Fhim.
