OL,6,F"Far from discharging its
OL,7,Finternational obligations in law to
OL,8,Fconvene and conclude Sean's inquest,
OL,9,Fthe British Government has instead
OL,10,Fabandoned its legal obligations."
OL,12,FHe described the Legacy Act as an
OL,13,F"obscenity" and said opposition to it
OL,14,Fhad united all communities in Northern
OL,15,FIreland.
